---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy for whyismywebsiteslow.com.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-400">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>

    <div class="prose prose-invert mt-8 max-w-none prose-p:text-slate-300 prose-li:text-slate-300 prose-headings:text-slate-100 prose-strong:text-slate-100">
      <p>
        This Privacy Policy explains how whyismywebsiteslow.com ("we", "us") collects, uses, and shares information when
        you use our website and services (the "Service").
      </p>

      <h2>Information we collect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Account information</strong>: if you create an account, we collect information you provide.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage data</strong>: basic analytics and logs (for example, pages viewed, actions taken, and error logs).</li>
        <li><strong>Website URLs you scan</strong>: the URLs you submit for analysis and related scan/report metadata.</li>
        <li><strong>Payment information</strong>: payments are processed by our payment provider; we receive limited billing metadata (for example, plan, status, and transaction identifiers) but not full card details.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How we use information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Provide, maintain, and improve the Service.</li>
        <li>Generate and display performance reports you request.</li>
        <li>Prevent abuse, fraud, and security incidents.</li>
        <li>Communicate about service updates and billing-related notices.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Sharing</h2>
      <p>
        We share information with service providers that help us operate the Service (for example, hosting, analytics,
        and payments). We may also disclose information if required by law or to protect rights, safety, and security.
      </p>

      <h2>Data retention</h2>
      <p>
        We keep information as long as necessary for the purposes described above, including to comply with legal
        obligations, resolve disputes, and enforce agreements.
      </p>

      <h2>Your choices</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>You can stop using the Service at any time.</li>
        <li>You can request deletion of your account data where applicable.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Changes</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy from time to time by posting a new version on this page.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

